rows.label: qst200309_msg0001
rows.name:
What's that? Did I see
a Gogol, you ask?

rows.label: qst200309_msg0002
rows.name:
I saw it, alright. The shock of
it nearly made my back give out.

rows.label: qst200309_msg0003
rows.name:
To be honest... I only got a
glimpse, so I couldn't tell you
what kind of Gogol it was...

rows.label: qst200309_msg0004
rows.name:
Oh, that's right. I think it was a
bit smaller than a normal Gogol.

rows.label: qst200309_msg0005
rows.name:
But still, it's a rare thing for a
Gogol to appear inside the city.

rows.label: qst200309_msg0006
rows.name:
Gogols are clever monsters, you
see, so they don't usually get close
to places with lots of people.

rows.label: qst200309_msg0007
rows.name:
There must be some reason
for it, I'd wager.

rows.label: qst200309_msg0008
rows.name: Well, that's about all I know.

rows.label: qst200309_msg0009
rows.name:
You should try asking other
people for more details.
